snippet.textDisplay:
Its almost 2 years spending my time being a reveluv, and I will never regret my days that I've spend.

In 2015, I keep saying to other people that I hate them just bcs they make a weird song and having bad title track. Being an antis to them and feel disgusted everytime I listen to people who keep shouting rv name. In late 2017, i was scrolling down page on youtube, after that I was accidentally read the title of this video (why people keep hating on rv) and yeah something like that,i don't remember the title of that vdeo actually and I open that vdeo, watching it from the start until the end without even pause it. It was the day i realized, they are really something. Something thay I can't even tell everyone. RV facing too many hardships and even antis called them flop even after debut. I was crying almost about 1 hours. Not related but I just wanted to say that, I stanning rv at the same time I was stanning bts. I was watching bts vdeo (almost the same titled as rv vdeo). How tae was crying over his grandma and bts antis even trend hate hashtag about him. HYYH/WINGS concert are the best for me. Sorry for any misinformation/misinterpret and my poor english. I wanted to add some story abt how I can be an army. But i think this is not the right place to share my story.

Im so sorry KINGS & QUEENS you don't deserves me :((((

snippet.textDisplay: I’m here again and again with the thoughts of Wendy in my mind. I really miss her and I know everyone does. It really hurts that we ended 2019 with that tragic event and starting the new year without Wendy on stage.
